MC-SQLR Amplification: MS SQL Server Resolution Service enables reflected DDoS with 440x amplification
 
 
 
 
 
 Summary The MS SQL Server Resolution Service allows a client to interrogate a server hosting a SQL Server installation and to receive back detailed information about the SQL Server instances available on the server.  The client sends a one-byte request to the server, and the server responds with a variable-